PATENT NOTICE

The core technology of EpisodicRAG is the subject of a pending patent application
in Japan:

  Application Number: 特願2025-198943
  Title: Hierarchical Memory and Digest Generation System
  Filed: 2025

This patent application covers the 8-layer memory architecture and digest
generation processes implemented in this software.

